description:
There are times in our lives where the relationships which hold the sky above us, and which fundamentally ground us to our understanding of who we truly are.  

If you throw away your soul mate for a romp or deny your true nature, you may find happiness, or that you have broken 3 hearts at once... 
 A lie unfolded can find no common ground, this foray into bliss does not hold the sky and your roots do not grow within this.
 For even scorned , your old flame, your true love, holds more than a candle to your flame.

  If you have hurt someone you love, do be sure to mend time's wounds and seek Reconciliation before you both slip away.  You may find that your path was never one of exile, but one of forgiveness.

do not let the doubt flowing in the stream of consciousness guide you.  Take this cavern as a place of solace and respite, not one twisted by fear.

--self
